TECHNOLOGIES
============
ReactJS (lenguaje front-end)
NodeJS (lenguaje back-end)
WebPack (generate build and deploy in localhost)
Babel
Express (Para conectar a MongoDB)
Mongoose (mapear los modelos de datos)
API RESTful (es aquella que emplea todos los verbos HTTP (GET, POST, PUT y DELETE mayormente) )
aplicación CRUD (Create/Read/Update/Delete)
bodyParser (parsear JSON)
method-override (nos permite implementar y personalizar métodos HTTP40 )
JSON (formato de datos)
tcp-ping (for doing ping to a host)
cors (to allow format in request header)
flux (framework about states, based on actions, dispatchers, stores and views)

TOOLS
=====
Studio 3T for Mongodb (CLient DB)
Test Api Rest (chrome-extension://cokgbflfommojglbmbpenpphppikmonn/index.html#response you need chrome extension " restconsole")